---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Quest Labs — About">

<div class="about-hero">
  <div class="about-eyebrow">Quest Labs · The Creator</div>
  <h1 class="about-title">About</h1>
  <p class="about-sub">The practitioner-researcher behind the praxis.</p>
</div>

<div class="about-grid">
  <div class="about-image-block">
    <img src="/makeda.JPG" alt="Makēda Gershenson" class="about-photo" />
  </div>

  <div class="about-text-block">
    <div class="about-section-label">Makēda</div>
    <h2 class="about-name">Quest Prime · Practitioner-Researcher</h2>
    <p>Since 2008, Makēda Gershenson has been building playgrounds for the future. As founder of Quest Labs | Mosaics in the Making, she facilitates sandbox sessions and research collaborations that function less like classrooms and more like portals - places where play becomes possibility and constraints are composted.</p>
    <p>Her work dances at the intersection of education, workforce evolution, and radical foresight, weaving decolonial scholarship and embodied practice into experiences that move people from what they've inherited to what they're brave enough to create.</p>
    <p>Her approach holds tension tenderly and is rigorously playful toward co-crafting infrastructures of care.</p>
    <p>Whether facilitating sandbox sessions that crack open new capacities, conducting organizational research that remaps who holds power over tomorrow, or exploring how a single metaphor can unlock what once seemed impossible, Makēda creates the conditions for you to see the stories you've been living inside and then craft a different future together.</p>

    <div id="work-with-us" style="margin-top:3rem; padding-top:3rem; border-top:0.5px solid rgba(107,63,160,0.2);">

      <p style="font-size:11px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#B48FE0; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Work with Makēda</p>

      <h2 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size:2.2rem; font-weight:500; color:#FDFCFA; margin-bottom:1.5rem; line-height:1.2;">Three ways to bring<br>this work to your world</h2>

      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap:1rem; margin-bottom:2rem;">

        <div style="background:rgba(107,63,160,0.06); border:0.5px solid rgba(107,63,160,0.25); border-radius:4px; padding:1.5rem;">
          <div style="font-size:13px; font-weight:500; color:#FDFCFA; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">For your school or district</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px; color:#9A90B8; line-height:1.6;">Custom Sandbox Sessions, Sarkar Sandbox facilitation, STEEP Bingo for staff development, futures literacy workshops. Built around what your educators actually need.</div>
        </div>

        <div style="background:rgba(107,63,160,0.06); border:0.5px solid rgba(107,63,160,0.25); border-radius:4px; padding:1.5rem;">
          <div style="font-size:13px; font-weight:500; color:#FDFCFA; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">For your organization</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px; color:#9A90B8; line-height:1.6;">Organizational futures research, STEEP Bingo for leadership teams, participatory foresight facilitation, custom futures literacy experiences via Mosaics in the Making.</div>
        </div>

        <div style="background:rgba(107,63,160,0.06); border:0.5px solid rgba(107,63,160,0.25); border-radius:4px; padding:1.5rem;">
          <div style="font-size:13px; font-weight:500; color:#FDFCFA; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Sponsor a seat</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px; color:#9A90B8; line-height:1.6;">20 sponsored seats available for the Flip the Script Fall 2026 founding cohort. Fund an educator's place in the room. Pay it forward and materially disrupt systems of oppression and harm.</div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="mailto:questlabs.foresight@gmail.com?subject=Working%20with%20Quest%20Labs" class="cta-primary">Let's talk →</a>
        <a href="/educators#sponsored" class="cta-secondary">Sponsor a seat →</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="about-closing">
      <hr class="about-divider" />
      <p class="about-closing-text">This is what it looks like in practice.</p>
      <div class="about-closing-links">
        <a href="/program">Explore FLIP →</a>
        <a href="/about#work-with-us">Work with Makēda →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page-bridge" style="max-width:860px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; padding-left:2.5rem; padding-right:2.5rem;">
  <p>Want to experience the practice before reaching out?</p>
  <a href="https://lu.ma/questlabs" class="bridge-link">Find a Sandbox Session — open door, no commitment →</a>
  <a href="/educators" class="bridge-link" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">Educator? Flip the Script starts May 17 →</a>
</div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem 2rem 3rem;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .about-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.2s forwards;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-pale);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.4s forwards;
  }

  .about-sub {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.6s forwards;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 5rem auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-image-block {
    padding-right: 3rem;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-text-block {
    padding-left: 3rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
  }

  .about-section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-name {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .about-text-block p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-closing {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-closing-text {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem !important;
  }

  .about-closing-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-closing-links a {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--teal);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .about-closing-links a:hover {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .about-image-block {
      padding-right: 0;
    }

    .about-text-block {
      padding-left: 0;
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
